HEADWORD: Misthink
<hw>Mis*think"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Think</er>.]</ety> <def>To think wrongly.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧Adam <xex>misthought</xex> of her.⟦rdquo⟧
