==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Misthink
<hw>Mis*think"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To have erroneous thoughts or
judgment of; to think ill of.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

